when grandma could just zap

07:01.630 --> 07:04.122
her famous fruitcake
to her kiddies in Kalamazoo?

07:04.257 --> 07:06.624
How about the auto industry,
the airlines, big oil?!

07:06.760 --> 07:09.298
Global economy would go ass
over teakettle, that's what.

07:09.429 --> 07:12.263
Some extremely powerful people
ain't gonna like that,

07:12.390 --> 07:14.382
and they're gonna
come a-gunning for you.

07:14.517 --> 07:16.600
Isn't it kind of your job
to protect me?

07:16.728 --> 07:19.721
We kind of are, Doc.
From yourself.

07:19.856 --> 07:21.563
Shut it down
and hand it over,

07:21.691 --> 07:24.650
or we'll shut it down
and get real handsy about it.

07:24.778 --> 07:26.770
Ugh, this is crazy.
It's a free country.

07:26.905 --> 07:29.147
Mm-hmm.
Is it, now?

07:30.158 --> 07:31.774
What, are you gonna
torture me now?

07:31.910 --> 07:32.910
Brock, what the "F"?

07:33.036 --> 07:36.154
- It ain't like that, Doc.
- More like group therapy.

07:36.289 --> 07:38.326
But wait a minute!
Where are you going, Brock?!

07:38.458 --> 07:40.324
What's gonna happen to me?

07:40.460 --> 07:43.043
Hello? Brock?

07:43.171 --> 07:45.208
Judas!

07:48.301 --> 07:50.543
<i>Greetings, Dr. Venture.</i>

07:50.679 --> 07:53.797
<i>We've been watching you
for some time.</i>

07:53.932 --> 07:55.423
And you are...?

07:55.558 --> 07:59.051
<i>Oh, we've gone by many names
throughout the centuries.</i>

07:59.187 --> 08:01.600
<i>- The Knights Templar.
- The Illuminati.</i>

08:01.731 --> 08:04.644
<i>The Rothschild/Bilderberg
Super Sentinels.</i>

08:04.776 --> 08:09.066
<i>We... Well, we kind of
secretly control the world.</i>

08:09.197 --> 08:11.780
<i>Until now we've been happy
to remain in shadows</i>

08:11.908 --> 08:15.151
<i>insomuch as your business
has not interfered with ours,</i>

08:15.286 --> 08:18.825
<i>but this teleporter of yours,
it's really a game-changer.</i>

08:18.957 --> 08:20.914
What is this,
some kind of threat?

08:21.042 --> 08:24.001
<i>No, Dr. Venture,
an invitation.</i>

08:24.129 --> 08:26.416
<i>As we said,
we've been watching you,</i>

08:26.548 --> 08:30.462
<i>and we think you have what
it takes to become one of us.</i>

08:30.593 --> 08:33.176
<i>Think of it...
power beyond your imagining,</i>

08:33.304 --> 08:37.092
<i>untold riches,
your every desire fulfilled.</i>

08:37.225 --> 08:40.592
<i>And all you need do is give up
one little invention.</i>

08:40.729 --> 08:41.311
Ugh.

08:41.312 --> 08:43.645
<i>You don't have to
make your mind up now.</i>

08:43.773 --> 08:47.392
<i>As it happens, we're convening
in secret this very night,</i>

08:47.527 --> 08:49.644
<i>and we'd very much like
to meet you...</i>

08:49.779 --> 08:51.736
<i>in the flesh, as it were.</i>

08:51.865 --> 08:54.949
<i>Come.
See what we can offer you.</i>

08:55.076 --> 08:57.068
<i>Then decide.</i>

09:01.666 --> 09:02.666
<i>Otra vez.</i>

09:02.709 --> 09:04.996
Come on.
<i>MÃ¡s fuerte.</i>

09:06.463 --> 09:08.420
<i>Mucho mejor.
Tiempo fuera</i>, Manolo.

09:08.548 --> 09:10.130
Hey. How's your
super-heist meeting?

09:10.258 --> 09:12.796
Super fucked! This heist
is going down tonight.

09:12.927 --> 09:15.795
