the Glengarry wings.

09:31.071 --> 09:33.438
They're in the, uh,
basement, cave, whatever.

09:33.573 --> 09:36.111
- Find them!
- All right, all right! Hold on.

09:36.242 --> 09:38.700
Aerial reconnaissance.

09:38.828 --> 09:39.864
Dicks.

09:39.996 --> 09:42.158
