your eyebrows in there?

09:49.714 --> 09:50.830
Giddyap!

09:50.965 --> 09:52.456
Just a minute!

09:52.592 --> 09:53.952
- Okay, I found them.
- Great.

09:54.010 --> 09:55.217
Now get them over here fast.

09:55.345 --> 09:57.007
