13:15.169 --> 13:16.876
and then washed it down
with penis, so...

13:17.005 --> 13:18.245
Hey, if that's
what you're into.

13:18.339 --> 13:20.831
What? No!
Actually, I'm a little lost.

13:20.967 --> 13:22.503
Are you a member
of this, uh...

13:22.635 --> 13:25.423
Pseudo-religious
capitalist crony club?

13:25.555 --> 13:26.555
God, no.

13:26.681 --> 13:28.138
Just an anonymous
working girl

13:28.266 --> 13:30.508
here to service
the masters of the universe.

13:30.643 --> 13:32.259
Oh. Ohh.

13:32.395 --> 13:34.978
This gig was a lot easier
before they inducted the guy

13:35.106 --> 13:36.563
who invented Viagra,
I'll tell you.

13:36.691 --> 13:40.105
That's him over there next
to big oil and big tobacco.

13:40.236 --> 13:41.898
They're the ones
double-teaming Patty.

13:42.030 --> 13:44.272
Uh, do I know you?

13:44.407 --> 13:46.444
No.
You don't want to do that here.

13:46.576 --> 13:52.038
Uh, then perhaps we should
go somewhere more private.

13:52.165 --> 13:54.407
May I borrow her?

13:54.584 --> 13:58.203
Meet me by the tapestries
in 20 minutes.

14:09.265 --> 14:11.006
Presto change-o, I'm in!

14:11.142 --> 14:12.142
<i>Good!</i>

14:12.185 --> 14:14.472
<i>Find the mainframe and get
that transmitter plugged in.</i>

14:15.605 --> 14:17.346
Ooh!
Someone's coming!

14:19.233 --> 14:22.943
It's Samson!
What do I do?

14:23.071 --> 14:25.438
Dude, what?!
He's not supposed to be here!

14:25.573 --> 14:26.842
Oh, good Lord.
This ain't good.

14:26.866 --> 14:27.986
Ah, that's it.
Let me at him.

14:28.034 --> 14:29.696
<i>Hold your position, Ramburglar.</i>

14:29.827 --> 14:31.467
You bust in before
I've hacked the system,

14:31.579 --> 14:33.115
you'll trigger
a total lockdown.

14:33.247 --> 14:34.704
Monarch, plan B.

14:34.832 --> 14:36.869
Plan B?
What... What plan B?

14:37.001 --> 14:40.210
<i>God, did you pay, like,
no attention at the meeting?</i>

14:40.338 --> 14:41.338
<i>Proceed to
the Venture penthouse</i>

14:41.339 --> 14:42.750
<i>and create a diversion</i>

14:42.882 --> 14:45.374
<i>to draw Samson away
from the lab stat!</i>

14:45.510 --> 14:47.923
- Okay!
- Uh! I'm here, I'm here.

14:48.054 --> 14:50.216
- Subway took forever.
- Oh, thank God!

14:50.348 --> 14:52.510
- You got my wings, Mr. Late?
- Yeah, yeah, here.

14:52.642 --> 14:54.508
Dude, can I use
Copycat's bathroom?

14:54.644 --> 14:57.307
Yeah, whatever. Wait.
What... What the fuck is this?

14:57.438 --> 14:59.475
It's your wings. That was
gonna be my cover story.

14:59.607 --> 15:02.224
Your cover story is
I shit myself?

15:02.360 --> 15:03.712
Hey, you make a lie
embarrassing enough,

15:03.736 --> 15:04.977
and nobody questions it.

15:05.113 --> 15:07.105
Eh, all right.

15:10.451 --> 15:11.908
Samson's going
for the teleporters.

15:12.036 --> 15:14.356
We ain't got time for this
flying fuck-up to make his move.

15:14.455 --> 15:16.037
I've got an idea.

15:18.918 --> 15:21.001
H.E.L.P.eR.
Heya, buddy.

15:21.129 --> 15:24.293
I didn't see you...
Ah, geez, did Doc paint you?

15:25.925 --> 15:29.214
Nice work, Presto.
I'm in.

15:29.345 --> 15:31.632
- H.E.L.P.eR.?
- Uh...

15:33.391 --> 15:35.974
Dot, do something!

15:42.024 --> 15:43.140
Oh, good Lord.

15:43.276 --> 15:44.892
Dottie, what in the "H"
did you do?

15:45.027 --> 15:46.268
I'm not doing that!

15:46.404 --> 15:48.487
It's some kind of
emergency evac or something!

15:48.614 --> 15:49.855
I can't stop it.

15:55.913 --> 15:57.620
Aha! I got one!

15:57.748 --> 16:00.957
Good for you, toy man.
Now you're gonna get dead.

16:11.554 --> 16:13.420
- Who needs a refill?
- Yeah!

16:13.556 --> 16:15.798
Rejiggered that
old emergency evac

16:15.933 --> 16:18.141
to send the goods
exactly where we want them.

16:18.269 --> 16:19.385
Swell hacking, Mac.

16:19.520 --> 16:21.136
Our little old decoy team

16:21.272 --> 16:23.730
must be in a whole heap
of hot water.

16:23.858 --> 16:26.316
That was the plan, my man.

16:30.114 --> 16:32.777
Not a good time!

16:32.909 --> 16:35.447
Dude, dude, you got to abort!
Abort!

16:35.578 --> 16:37.615
Copycat has got
another heist team!

16:37.747 --> 16:39.955
You're being set up!
You're decoys!

16:40.082 --> 16:41.082
You're

16:41.167 --> 16:44.160
You're breaking up.
Wait! What? Aah!

16:46.297 --> 16:48.505
Oh! Ah!

16:48.633 --> 16:51.046
Owie.

16:51.177 --> 16:53.294
Enh! Aah!

16:53.429 --> 16:55.421
Ow!

16:57.683 --> 17:00.016
What? No way.

17:07.151 --> 17:11.566
"The Unicorn is in Captivity
and No Longer Dead,"

17:11.696 --> 17:13.404
Late 15th century.

17:13.532 --> 17:15.900
A truly exquisite piece.

17:16.035 --> 17:18.071
And such an apt metaphor.

17:18.204 --> 17:21.038
Because, let me guess,
I'm the unicorn,

17:21.165 --> 17:22.326
and now I'm your prisoner.

17:22.458 --> 17:24.915
No, you're looking
at it all wrong.

17:25.044 --> 17:28.127
Look at that little unicorn,
the beatific smile.

17:28.256 --> 17:29.872
He's happy now.

17:30.007 --> 17:33.626
He gets to live
in a beautiful garden.

17:33.761 --> 17:35.047
Yeah, in a cage.

17:35.179 --> 17:37.045
A protective barrier.

17:37.181 --> 17:39.218
No one's hunting him anymore,

17:39.350 --> 17:42.138
nor can he hurt anyone
with that horn of his.

17:42.270 --> 17:43.932
Yeah, well,
if it's all the same to you,

17:44.063 --> 17:45.474
this little unicorn

17:45.606 --> 17:47.472
would rather take his chances
in the wilderness

17:47.608 --> 17:50.191
with his sweet-ass teleporter.

17:52.530 --> 17:54.237
Oh, I'm afraid that's not

17:54.365 --> 17:56.823
one of your options,
Dr. Venture.

17:56.951 --> 18:00.444
No doubt you've read
"The Lady or the Tiger"?

18:00.580 --> 18:02.287
Well, not word for word, but...

18:02.415 --> 18:05.032
Behind door number one,
the lady.

18:05.167 --> 18:07.375
I believe you two
have already met.

18:07.503 --> 18:09.961
Give up your teleporter
and join us,

18:10.089 --> 18:11.625
and she's all yours,

18:11.757 --> 18:13.589
as is anything else
you could ever desire.

18:13.718 --> 18:17.883
Behind door number two,
meet Tiger.

18:18.014 --> 18:21.007
Tiger has desires, too.

18:21.142 --> 18:22.349
Wha... What?

18:22.476 --> 18:24.513
Please tell me
this is another metaphor.

18:24.645 --> 18:27.604
Cold, hard truth,
Dr. Venture.

18:27.732 --> 18:32.147
In this world,
it's fuck or be fucked.

18:32.278 --> 18:35.362
So which will it be?

18:35.489 --> 18:37.822
Just go, Rambo.
We got one of them.

18:37.950 --> 18:39.532
No, job was for both.

18:39.660 --> 18:40.971
You're gonna drill
this boy's knees

18:40.995 --> 18:43.112
till he tells us
where the other one went.

18:45.041 --> 18:47.283
Oh, you are good, Monarch.

18:47.418 --> 18:49.455
Aah!

18:50.838 --> 18:52.670
Oh, dang, I'm hit!

18:54.508 --> 18:56.044
Aah! Uh, uh!

18:57.345 --> 18:59.803
- Oh, God.
- Oh, he's coming to! Grab it!

18:59.930 --> 19:01.046
I... How?!

19:01.182 --> 19:03.014
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

19:04.518 --> 19:07.056
Ahhh.
Amateurs.

19:07.188 --> 19:08.269
I need backup.

19:08.397 --> 19:10.810
Hostiles have taken the package,
and I'm in pursuit.

19:10.941 --> 19:13.649
Come on out of there
right now, Monarch,

19:13.778 --> 19:15.485
and I promise
I'll only wound you.

19:15.613 --> 19:16.694
Just come out of there!

19:16.822 --> 19:18.859
There really is no way out!

19:31.754 --> 19:35.794
Copycat 3 to Copycat Prime,
the package is secure.

19:35.925 --> 19:36.961
Aah!

19:40.763 --> 19:44.006
How in the...?
This is just bananagans!

19:53.025 --> 19:55.517
Listen, you guys don't know me,
but you got to trust me.

19:55.653 --> 19:57.144
You guys...
What the fuck?!

19:57.279 --> 19:59.862
- Dude, who the hell are you?
- I'm... I'm with the Monarch!

19:59.990 --> 20:01.218
You guys
got to get out of here!

20:01.242 --> 20:02.403
This whole thing
is a setup!

20:02.535 --> 20:04.572
- What did you do to Driver X?
- What? I didn't...

20:04.704 --> 20:06.570
There wasn't even
a guy in there.

20:06.706 --> 20:08.288
Start...
Start the truck, Chief.

20:08.416 --> 20:10.248
Samson is right on our tails.
I think

20:10.376 --> 20:12.242
Aah! Aaaah!

20:12.378 --> 20:14.119
You're Driver X now, fatty.

20:14.255 --> 20:16.622
Take this!
I'll slow him down!

20:16.757 --> 20:19.295
Presto change-o!

20:21.220 --> 20:24.054
Oh, stop!

20:24.181 --> 20:26.013
Stupid!

20:26.142 --> 20:27.929
Aaah!

20:28.686 --> 20:31.975
Whoa! W-T-F?!

20:33.774 --> 20:36.141
Aaaaah!

20:36.277 --> 20:37.563
Geez!

20:40.114 --> 20:42.572
Copycat 3 to Copycat Base,

20:42.700 --> 20:44.566
got a big old mayday
on my hands here.

20:44.702 --> 20:47.160
Holy mackerel, the engine
is shot, literal like.

20:47.288 --> 20:48.768
Abort-a-rooney time.

20:52.710 --> 20:55.293
Well, now doesn't that
just put a turd in your soup?

20:59.717 --> 21:01.549
Come on!

21:01.677 --> 21:03.168
Aah!

21:06.432 --> 21:07.639
Aaah!

21:17.443 --> 21:19.480
- 'Sup?
- Hey.

21:28.996 --> 21:31.989
Move, move,
move, move, move, move!

22:04.949 --> 22:08.283
Ah!

22:08.410 --> 22:09.742
You were right!

22:09.870 --> 22:13.409
Oh, this is the best decision
I ever made.

22:13.541 --> 22:17.205
I'm the king of the world!

22:17.336 --> 22:19.669
Ahh.

22:19.797 --> 22:21.629
Get a nerd laid,

22:21.757 --> 22:24.625
and they think
they're masters of the universe.

